702975f-a.title: Brooklyn: Alice Court - Atlantic Avenue
702975f-a.text:
2 to 18 Alice Court, east side, north from Atlantic Avenue.. Alice Court is a short, dead-end street, running north 150 feet
from Atlantic Avenue.
September 13, 1940
P. L. Sperr
